UK: UK gilt auction announcement -- full details.UK gilt auction announcement -- full details.The following issue was announcedby the Bank of EnglandISSUER: H M TreasuryAMOUNT: 2.5 billion stgCOUPON: 7.5 percentMATURITY: 2006AUCTION DATE: August 28NOTES: The new gilts are fully fungible with stock already in issue and will be strippable when an official gilts strips facility is introduced. Provision for non-resident tax exemption but, as announced on August 13, dividends will be paid gross of tax to all holders with effect from June 7 1997.